  "response": "One essential characteristic that every leader should possess is empathy. Empathy allows leaders to understand and relate to the feelings and perspectives of their team members, fostering trust and collaboration. By being empathetic, leaders can create a supportive environment, motivate their teams effectively, and navigate challenges with a greater awareness of the emotional dynamics at play. This quality not only enhances communication but also helps in building a strong, cohesive team culture.",
